ilestone":null,"comments":2,"created_at":"2019-11-18T10:26:56Z","updated_at":"2020-07-08T21:16:05Z","closed_at":"2020-07-08T21:16:04Z","author_association":"NONE","active_lock_reason":null,"body":"## Describe the proposal\r\nSimple helper method to get or create an experiment, seems it's very handy when creating or reusing the mlflow experiments.\r\n\r\n### Motivation\r\nTo simply the usage pattern and bring the common usage patterns with in the library.\r\n\r\n### Proposed Changes\r\n\r\nHere is the relevant code change involved.\r\n\r\n```python\r\n\r\n# Set the tracking URL.\r\nmlflow.set_tracking_uri(\"http://127.0.0.1:5000\")\r\n\r\n\r\n# Helper fun.\r\ndef get_or_create_experiment(name, artifact_location=None):\r\n    experiment = mlflow.get_experiment_by_name(name)\r\n    if not experiment:\r\n        experiment_id = mlflow.create_experiment(name, artifact_location)\r\n        experiment = mlflow.get_experiment(experiment_id)\r\n    return experiment\r\n\r\n\r\nmlflow.get_or_create_experiment = get_or_create_experiment\r\n\r\n```\r\n","closed_by":{"login":"AveshCSingh","id":1208791,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEyMDg3OTE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1208791?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/AveshCSingh","html_url":"https://github.com/AveshCSingh","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/AveshCSingh/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/AveshCSingh/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/AveshCSingh/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/AveshCSingh/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/AveshCSingh/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/AveshCSingh/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/AveshCSingh/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/AveshCSingh/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/AveshCSingh/received_events","type":"User","site_ad